Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:38.82,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Besides, baseball's all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Speaking of baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The famous poet, Shiki Masaoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:43.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...apparently loved baseball a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He played catcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...until he was too ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And he took his childhood name, Noboru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...wrote it using the characters for baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and pronounced it Noball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:55.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:59.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The winners of the Major League\N are called the world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Talking about the Japan Series reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:05.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Even when it only includes American teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:11.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, they should beat our team before\N they call themselves world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's awfully pumped up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It sure stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:17.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:18.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:18.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Teach me how to do these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You asking a question about schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Some of these problems are quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:36.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's cause they're from an arcade quiz game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with academic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And put more effort into your studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're applying for college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I may be like this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but they call me a sage over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:54.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...just enroll in that whatever academy of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:56.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Which is why I didn't get enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How long were you up playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You say you're always in bed by eleven, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:03.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Now I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.99,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,454.5)\fad(300,0)\fnJose Fernandez\fs36\b1\bord5\blur0.6\c&HFB69FF&\3c&HFAE7F9&}Sleeping helps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.99,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,454.5)\fad(300,0)\fnJose Fernandez\fs36\b1\bord5\blur0.6\c&HFB69FF&\3c&HFAE7F9&}you grow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking when I looked at Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but you haven't grown much considering how much you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:14.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's what Big Sister said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm really sensitive about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.50,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,75)\bord4\b1\blur0.5\fs40\fn@A-OTF Shin Maru Go Pro M\c&HDD7B37&\3c&HFFFEFF&}That night, around 9 o'clock
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:21.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My name is Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is this the Iwasaki residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:27.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,May I speak with Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She already went to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she always sleep this early?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're having fun singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:58.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:00.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll let my father know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,After the ground-breaking ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:10.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Please, there you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm underage, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They can't see you gesturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's just a force of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:27.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:32.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When I'm on the phone, I have to concentrate so I stop gaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but then my empty hand starts feeling lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:43.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I was using a roller to get rid of dust the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:44.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Roll! Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that can get pretty addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:50.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like random doodling or menial chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:56.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Once you get off the phone, that stuff gets old really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:06:00.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's kinda depressing when only the area around you is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You could just finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My passion fades with the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So you just leave it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That guy's kinda stinky, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess it's okay every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:14.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,**cky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Po***!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:17.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I used to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:19.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...back in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:23.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Speaking of things we did when we were little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I used to stir my yogurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and go, "Bread factory!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Haven't heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't be embarrassed. Just 'fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,About that game I lent you back during first semester...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Someone else wants to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:47.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is it for the squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've lent a bunch to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I should get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you sure are amazing, Hiiragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:57.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:01.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The other day, I found these games and\N didn't remember who I borrowed them from...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:04.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:07.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And there are some I lent to other people that I've forgotten about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're way too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:09.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be a Law of Equal Lending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's a universal principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:21.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:24.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's u—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:28.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Potemkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:35.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It was something super important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't forget it if it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the numbers for the Autumn Jumbo Lottery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but mine were all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess it's not so easy to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I sent in a bunch of postcards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I didn't win any prizes from the drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When you never win...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:05.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you start to wonder if the vendors or\N editors are running some kind of scam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:06.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be so suspicious of other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:11.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna call it a night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:16.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go to the bathroom first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They tell me that I talk to myself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But that don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was really sleepy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:34.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...so why am I so awake after that weird joke?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.78,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,70)\fn@Iwata Maru Gothic Pro M-Kami\fs30\c&H000000&\blur0.4}Next day, dead of night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really can't do this at night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not feeling it tonight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:42.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should get to bed while I'm dozing off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:47.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was really sleepy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:55.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...so why am I so awake just 'cause it's cold under the covers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.11,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,70)\fn@Iwata Maru Gothic Pro M-Kami\fs30\c&H000000&\blur0.4}The day {\fs33}after that{\fs39}, dead of night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's useless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's warm tonight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I can fall asleep quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My legs are really hot for some reason...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:08.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't fall asleep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does this only happen to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:19.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's the season for baked sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:20.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:24.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know, so don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you'll gain weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You still said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Once I've made eye contact with the guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...it'd be rude not to buy one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:34.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,"Will she buy one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,"My feelings will be hurt if she doesn't."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you make eye contact at Comiket...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...it's really hard to put a book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You don't care when other people have\N no idea what you're talking about, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:49.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:52.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about when you're hanging around a circle's booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When you pick up a book in front of a sales rep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you feel pretty bad if you leave without buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you still put it back, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's been an increase in the number\N of light novels being adapted to anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:06.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The novel I lent you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...has already had three anime adaptations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And there should be a new volume coming out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've watched the anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I haven't read the novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Too much text makes me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:17.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:21.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't the games you always play have a lot more text?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:24.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They should, but it's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:27.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It'd really help if they released them in a visual novel format.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:27.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:28.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:31.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When are they doing the fourth season of the anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:32.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:52.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Th-The lid always ends up crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, some people are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess it's clumsiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:00.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:04.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You share some cute flaws with Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You sure are amazing, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What do I do, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Now I can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:16.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I used my usual strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You sure are a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can't open the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hand it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:30.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How about we just tear it along the notches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:35.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,O-One sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:37.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll open it so hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We can just tear along the notches or use scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, that would hurt my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Or make me feel like a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, is it a mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Mosquito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:05.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't you get annoyed when you know something's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:07.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Even when you haven't been bitten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Once you know it's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:10.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you must take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's the instinct of a hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If a guy in the same year professed his love for Yu-chan or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:24.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't that guy be a lolicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They're in the same class year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so technically, they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:33.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But in this case, it feels like appearance holds more weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Say, if...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you were a 30-year-old who\N looked like someone in grade school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:41.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then you could say the guy likes older women...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is a complicated issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's hard to come up with a strict definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're definitely my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:50.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami would have just ended it with, "Who cares?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So what about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.24,0:12:57.18,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnI hate Comic Sans\c&HA28CFF&\3c&H141414&\blur0.7\fs60\bord0\b1\pos(74.667,84.833)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:57.18,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnI hate Comic Sans\c&HA28CFF&\3c&H141414&\blur0.7\fs60\bord6\b1\pos(74.667,84.833)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You fell in love with Mom...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.18,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnI hate Comic Sans\c&H59B7FF&\3c&H141414&\blur0.7\fs60\bord0\b1\pos(664,72)}Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.18,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnI hate Comic Sans\c&H59B7FF&\3c&H141414&\blur0.7\fs60\bord6\b1\pos(664,72)}Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and you dote on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...which means you're a lolicon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.56,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hold it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's not entirely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not limited to little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I also like normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:07.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So you should say that I'm {\i1}also{\i0} a lolicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, it basically depends on the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Either way, you fail as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:13.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know how you're always so clingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:19.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Would you still be like that if I were a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:22.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I totally understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad I'm a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:30.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I think the bath should be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You go first, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:33.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He chased her away 'cause he was looking bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,About Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:43.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She was short...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and your childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't she like a character out of a gal game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She was adorable since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can understand why you fell for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but why did she marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was like, "You wouldn't accept me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I ended up as a gal game lover!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And she just said yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't that coercion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:08.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the only reason, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:14.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And she was really happy when you were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:14.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this mole make her look like you, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She has your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can definitely tell she's our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:26.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But I hope she doesn't grow up like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I hope she doesn't inherit my height...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...or your personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Pretty harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:35.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But why did you suddenly mention her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely without Mom around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:51.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You create as much excitement as two people would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And Yu-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanata...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konata's grown up to be a good girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.81,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866,103.5)\fn@Iwata Gyousho Pro-Kami B\c&H4EB451&}A little geek
Dialogue: 3,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.81,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866,103.5)\fn@Iwata Gyousho Pro-Kami B\bord2\blur0.7\3c&HDCF5F5&}A little geek
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.81,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866,103.5)\fn@Iwata Gyousho Pro-Kami B\bord4\blur0.7\3c&H88DBF8&}A little geek
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though she's not as normal as you wanted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Please don't die before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,For now, I have no intention of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:13.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kanata died young...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but she said she was happy and smiled at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:22.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's hard on those left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I want to be like that at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:25.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So how do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:28.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Death by moe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:33.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're definitely going to have a bizarre death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:38.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I bought a digital camera for work today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.34,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I haven't been back in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:01.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.87,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder what...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:02.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Geez! I'm in the middle of a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.50,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...they're doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay! Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And Dad, you're way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:17.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're so heartless, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:21.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're taking photos to commemorate this new camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Didn't you buy this for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.52,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.52,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sou-kun hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:25.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One more picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:26.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.35,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's right, you never did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.61,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...pay much attention to what other people wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:32.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.45,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You really haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:43.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You feel more and more like Kanata when I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:44.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:48.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't just blurt out risqué statements!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:51.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can see what Mom had to put up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.59,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.56,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your dad may be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:57.47,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...but don't turn into a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:02.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Teach me that one game once you clear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:06.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That one's surprisingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.52,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I think I made a wrong choice somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.44,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They play games together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.57,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...so it looks like they're getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:13.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't make it to the H-scene for the character I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.40,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.90,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you letting your daughter play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.03,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.70,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.37,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aren't you teaching her the wrong things, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:27.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why did Mom choose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're just a perverted, lolicon, old geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,People usually don't go for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's a little harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You don't go easy on your old man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:37.76,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.84,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kanata had really good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.84,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You were always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.47,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Always making me almost forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.90,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...why I chose to spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Even though I failed as a human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:52.78,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...my life with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:55.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...there was one thing I was absolutely sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:00.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One thing you were absolutely sure about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the one who loved Kanata most in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.64,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:20.35,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I just can't beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.70,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.841\blur0.7\fs40\fn@A-OTF MidashiMinMA31-AnoHana\b1\pos(880,370.5)\c&H2C394F&\frx10\fry3}Results for the \NNew Writer Award
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:50.70,TS/Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.841\blur0.7\fs40\fn@A-OTF MidashiMinMA31-AnoHana\b1\c&H2C394F&\pos(839.334,534.167)\frx8\fry0}No \Nrecipients
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.97,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He accepts my good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.38,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He's willing to show both...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.45,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...his good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:09.72,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The place I feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:13.82,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The place that lets me feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:16.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:18.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's enough reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's take another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll do one with Yu-chan later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:25.11,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The fact that I can no longer be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:24.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And that would be more than one picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.91,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...hurts a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:26.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You bought this for your hobby, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:30.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:35.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm just testing it out before I take pictures for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.00,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:36.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.84,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If I can live on inside them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:43.47,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...the way the two of them exist inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.81,ls_alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...I'll continue to watch over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:47.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:51.39,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}May the ones who brought me so much joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.11,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...be blessed with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:54.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.29,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wonder if they'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:01.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:02.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There's a shadow back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A real ghost picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.33,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.71,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,I'm done with my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:12.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yu—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yu-Yu-Yu-Yu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:14.84,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,L-L-Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:17.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,D-Delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:20.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We have to delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.67,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:23.76,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:24.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Deleting it isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:27.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't we have to burn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.56,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:33.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Now that I've talked with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:35.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I have a different impression of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:38.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but Mina-rin still seems a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:41.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But she's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:45.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:46.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:47.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:49.99,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Those two are really close.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You had classroom duty today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:52.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Was the teacher still in the faculty office?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.24,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}This would be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yutaka, your tie is crooked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:56.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-Big Sister..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:57.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mustn't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm looking at my friends weird again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it's been building up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:06.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:08.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Can't find them anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And you can't find their managers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, they're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:18.19,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:18.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,670)}Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.52,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,610)}It's rolling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:22.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling about this show from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.57,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:22.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I actually refused in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But all that politics crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Grown-up issues and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.20,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:30.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:31.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:32.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:32.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:33.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Or the earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:34.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:35.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that the camera's rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:37.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:38.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:41.52,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:42.29,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:43.36,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nakajima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:46.49,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,Now, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:46.96,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,This time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.96,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,This time, it's the medley version!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.03,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't change when I blew the whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:05.20,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,You kept finishing Dentistman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:06.14,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:06.44,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:07.04,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:08.44,ls_ed_eng,,0,0,0,,Just switch.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.91,0:23:13.45,TS/EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(205.6,60.3)\fad(0,550)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:13.45,TS/EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(205.6,60.3)\fad(0,550)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:14.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Soujirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:15.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:16.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then Sou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:18.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll be heading off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:19.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:21.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:24.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to leave my body yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:25.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I'm sure I can learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:28.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun, you're talking about manga or anime again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:29.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:31.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:32.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.16,0:23:39.93,TS/EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs60\bord4\alpha&HEA&\t(0,600,\alpha&H00&)\pos(982.191,88.676)}「A Fine Line」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:39.93,TS/EpTitle,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur0.7\fs60\bord4\alpha&HEA&\t(0,600,\alpha&H00&)\pos(982.191,88.676)}「A Fine Line」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A Fine Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:35.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't fly with all the turbulence!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:38.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:42.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,
